                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-183-18351123 t18351123-183-punishment-144"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Fourth Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant</hi>.</p>
